<div id="teamfox" style="margin-top: 25px;">
<h2>Team Fox</h2>
<p><a href="https://www.michaeljfox.org/get-involved/teamfox.php">Team Fox</a> is the grassroots community fundraising program at The Michael J. Fox Foundation. Each year more than 2,000 members worldwide turn their passions and interests into unique fundraising events and athletic feats to further Parkinson's research.</p>
<ul class="videoList">
<li><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mhlusidkquM" class="fancybox-media">Welcome to Team Fox</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EwjU7vwOKlI" class="fancybox-media">A Tour of Your Participant Center</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eJaxDt6HBBg" class="fancybox-media">Tour de Fox</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
