<div id="livingwith">
<h2>Parkinson's Progression Marker's Initiative</h2>
<p>The Parkinson's Progression Markers Initiative is a landmark study launched in 2010 to find biomarkers â€” disease indicators that are critical missing links in the search for better Parkinson's treatments. Learn how MJFF is leading this effort and how you can play a role in it.</p>
<ul class="videoList">
<li><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nnExjYitZPc" class="fancybox-media">Intro to PPMI and the LP Procedure</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qQ8zPXN32tc" class="fancybox-media">The Search for a Biomarker</a></li>
</ul>
