<div id="webinars" style="float: left; margin-top: 10px;">
<h2>Webinars</h2>
<p>Our interactive Third Thursdays Webinar series, moderated by Dave Iverson, MJFF contributing editor and Patient Council member, tackles top-of-mind issues in Parkinson's research and care. Each webinar is grounded in the latest research on the topic of the month, with discussion of implications for living well with PD today. Panelists comprise a patient, clinician and researcher.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><a href="/page.html?hot-topics-webinar-series"> <img src="/files/orange-play.png" style="width: 20px; position: relative; top: 6px; padding-right: 5px;" /> View our archive of recent webinars and register for our next online event. </a></p>
